://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britains-anxious-young-adults-struggle-with-modern-workplace-demands-warns-uk-govt-advisor/articleshow/131294499.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britains-anxious-young-adults-struggle-with-modern-workplace-demands-warns-uk-govt-advisor/articleshow/131294499.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T21:41:42+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131294510,imgsize-39734.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Promised to return for dinner, never came back: Indian-origin man killed in NZ highway crash]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131293473.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/promised-to-return-for-dinner-never-came-back-indian-origin-ramandeep-dhillon-killed-in-new-zealand-highway-crash/articleshow/131293473.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/promised-to-return-for-dinner-never-came-back-indian-origin-ramandeep-dhillon-killed-in-new-zealand-highway-crash/articleshow/131293473.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T19:47:06+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131293497,imgsize-203232.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Trump turnaround: Open the straits, close the war]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131293243.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A new understanding with Iran is emerging to reopen the Strait of Hormuz. This comes after weeks of military escalation. The United States seeks to prevent global economic disruption from energy shipment issues. An agreement is reportedly nearing finalization, though details remain unclear. Iran denies commitments to give up uranium or unconditionally reopen the straits.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-turnaround-open-the-straits-close-the-war/articleshow/131293243.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-turnaround-open-the-straits-close-the-war/articleshow/131293243.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T19:13:43+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Chidanand Rajghatta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131293262,imgsize-116792.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian man Parminderpal Singh arrested by ICE in US, may face deportation]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131292389.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-man-parminderpal-singh-arrested-by-ice-in-los-angeles-over-criminal-record-may-face-deportation/articleshow/131292389.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/indian-man-parminderpal-singh-arrested-by-ice-in-los-angeles-over-criminal-record-may-face-deportation/articleshow/131292389.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T17:42:30+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131292444,imgsize-182846.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Champions League Final: Starmer urges UK broadcaster to make Arsenal vs PSG clash free to watch]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131293161.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description>