 least 24 people and injuring over 50. The blast, which occurred near Quetta, also damaged nearby vehicles and buildings. Authorities declared an emergency in Quetta hospitals and placed institutions on high alert.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-train-blast-dozens-killed-several-injured-in-quetta-explosion-near-railway-track/articleshow/131289475.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-train-blast-dozens-killed-several-injured-in-quetta-explosion-near-railway-track/articleshow/131289475.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T12:09:28+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131289523,imgsize-830756.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[France bans Israel minister Ben-Gvir over mocking detained Gaza flotilla activists]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131289305.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/france-bans-israel-minister-ben-gvir-over-mocking-detained-gaza-flotilla-activists/articleshow/131289305.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/france-bans-israel-minister-ben-gvir-over-mocking-detained-gaza-flotilla-activists/articleshow/131289305.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T11:56:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI News Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131289426,imgsize-72806.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[From Hormuz to nuclear talks - what to expect in the 60-day US-Iran ceasefire proposal]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131288866.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A potential 60-day ceasefire extension between the US and Iran is nearing, aiming to reopen the Strait of Hormuz and allow Iranian oil exports. This deal, brokered by Pakistan, includes lifting US port blockades and sanctions waivers, contingent on Iran negotiating its nuclear program and ending the Israel-Hezbollah conflict. Global oil markets are closely monitoring developments.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/from-hormuz-to-nuclear-talks-what-to-expect-in-the-60-day-us-iran-ceasefire-proposal/articleshow/131288866.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/from-hormuz-to-nuclear-talks-what-to-expect-in-the-60-day-us-iran-ceasefire-proposal/articleshow/131288866.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T10:32:57+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131288889,imgsize-804993.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Obsession with our country's most cherished structure': Trump reacts to White House shooting]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131288789.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US President Donald Trump praised the Secret Service and law enforcement for their swift action in neutralizing a gunman near the White House. The suspect, identified as Nasire Best, was killed after firing at agents. Trump highlighted the incident's importance for future presidential security, referencing a previous security breach.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/obsession-with-our-countrys-most-cherished-structure-trump-reacts-to-white-house-shooting/articleshow/131288789.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/obsession-with-our-countrys-most-cherished-structure-trump-reacts-to-white-house-shooting/articleshow/131288789.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T10:21:35+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131288812,imgsize-966519.cms"/></item></channel></rss>